'''Love Police Records''' is an [[independent record label]] based in [[Surry Hills, New South Wales]].  Originally started by Brian Taranto as a concept born from an ironic tshirt design, who was then joined by [[Andy Kent]] ([[You Am I]]).  

The motto for Love Police Records is simple: <blockquote>''stop talkin crap, record it, package it, put it out... someone will like it.''</blockquote> 

Love Police Records are distributed by [[Reverberation (record label)|Reverberation]] in Australia and [[New Zealand]]. 

== Artists ==
* [[The Rolling Blackouts]]
* [[The Cops (band)|The Cops]]

